Publisher: Lancer Books, Inc.

First Lancer Edition, 1966

Cover Art: Gray Morrow

Plot Synopsis (of cover): Tarzan, tired of adventuring with Jane and the apes, is itching for new challenges to meet. He strikes out on his own to battle against a sex cult of Blue Man Group worshipers at their annual carnival in the middle of the ocean.
